		<li><strong>Sustainable Wood:</strong> Choose FSC-certified lumber when possible</li>
		<li><strong>Longevity:</strong> Investing in durable materials reduces replacement frequency</li>
		<li><strong>Local Sourcing:</strong> Reduces transportation impact</li>
